{
  "stem": "22944.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, on one or two incidents, when I was walking to my auntie, I took a Star of David, and I used to see the gendarmerie, or the Hlinka army passing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they used to always, have a pencil-- a pen-- examining if this is sewn on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But mine was never sewn on, and I used to just take it off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, looking back, I can't believe it, that a child had so much courage not to put the Star of David.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then, on one occasion, my auntie asked me to go to grocery, and buy this-- didn't like to go any more-- to get some milk and cheese.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they really cursed me there-- grocery-- filthy, dirty Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Things like that I experienced an awful lot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But, strange enough, I must have been kind of a dream child wandering around.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because when the youth movement arrived to Nitra, lorries of young youth, the German youth movement, with a uniform like scouts uniform, arrive our town, I was so elevated, so happy.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were coming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And all the Slovak kids-- and they wave these flags, welcoming the occupation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Really, nobody actually knew what the occupation is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I was just gazing and looking at them, and quite envious.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, they look so lovely-- kids like 13, 14-year-old youths, and all blond, and all nicely dressed and singing, and-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --not realizing at all what it was all about.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And to such extent now-- now reached stage that I used to-- couldn't find any friends to play.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I used to go to a park.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The park I used to go to play was in Nitra, near us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was a lovely park.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
